---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap px-2.5 py-2.5">
    <div class="marquee-content">
      !! WELCOME TO EISING.NET !!&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;YOUR ONE-STOP DESTINATION FOR ALL THINGS "EISING" (SPECIFICALLY SHANE)
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mx-auto mb-4 mt-8 w-[min(95%,1100px)] border-10 border-double border-[#ffde59] bg-black/75 p-6 text-white shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,0,128,0.4)]">
    <div class="mb-5 border-[6px] border-retro-mint bg-[rgba(2,20,8,0.85)] px-4 py-3 text-center font-mono text-retro-mint shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(30,255,142,0.5)] [border-style:groove]">
      <span class="block text-base font-bold tracking-[0.2em]">VOTED #1 SHANE-RELATED WEBSITE</span>
      <p class="body-copy mt-2 text-retro-pale">
        <strong>Please Wipe Your Feet</strong> and don't forget to <strike>sign the guestbook!</strike>
      <br class="body-copy mt-2 text-retro-pale">
          like and subscribe? hit that bell? keep circulating the tapes??
      </br>
    </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-5 text-center font-display text-[1.75rem] tracking-[2px] text-[#ff9df9]">HAPPENINGS IN THE SHANE-O-SPHERE</h2>
    <div class="mb-6 grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr))] gap-4">
      <article class="border-[6px] border-[#fe61f6] bg-[rgba(50,0,70,0.7)] p-4 [border-style:groove]">
        <h3 class="mb-1 mt-0 text-[1.1rem] uppercase text-retro-gold">STILL AT SEA</h3>
        <ul class="body-copy pl-5">
          <li class="mb-1"><b>The Ship Show</b> continues to be a <i>ship-load</i> of work! Moving cautiously but forever hopeful through the choppiest waters and slowest winds.
          </li>
          <li class="mb-1">
            Will continue to post the occasional demo to the <b>Portfolio</b> page, so keep an eye out.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="border-[6px] border-[#fe61f6] bg-[rgba(50,0,70,0.7)] p-4 [border-style:groove]">
        <h3 class="mb-1 mt-0 text-[1.1rem] uppercase text-retro-gold">BUT WHAT ABOUT ME?</h3>
        <ul class="body-copy pl-5">
          <li class="mb-1">* Need music? Have money? Don't have money but still need music? That's what the <b>Contact</b> page is for!</li>
          <li class="mb-1">* Custom whodunit dinner parties continue to be available by commission (See Portfolio for samples). Tell 'em Shane sent you for a free clue.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="body-copy mb-6 border-4 border-dotted border-retro-pink bg-[rgba(255,78,203,0.08)] p-4">
      <h3 class="bold mt-0 text-retro-pink">Fresh Bytes</h3>
      <ul class="list-square pl-6">
        <li>- Demos of the full score of <em>Songs From West Egg</em> are now available for your listening pleasure in the Portfolio.</li>
        <li>- This website is a constant work-in-progress, so new oddities and curios may appear at any time. <span class="text-red-500">YOU HAVE BEEN WARNED!</span></li>
        <li>- Brainstorming ways to monetize this space: Unskippable ads? EISING.NET Members (get to skip the ads)? Sponsorship deals?</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="body-copy mb-6 border-4 border-retro-mint bg-[rgba(10,10,30,0.9)] p-4 font-mono shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(30,255,142,0.4)]">
      <strong class="text-retro-mint">EISING.NET &gt;_</strong> Access granted! While you're here…
      <ul class="list-square pl-6">
        <li>Have ChatGPT scrape the <a class="panel-link" href="/about">About</a> page to be disappointed by my lack of keywords and <span class="wordart-verb">action verbs</span>.</li>
        <li>Reach out for literally any reason on the <a class="panel-link" href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-6 border-4 border-dashed border-retro-cyan bg-[rgba(0,224,255,0.1)] p-3 text-center font-bold">
      ⚠️ WRONG WAY?? ⚠️ - Day-job related misadventures can be found at <span class="text-retro-cyan"><a class="panel-link" href="https://eising.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EISING.DEV</a></span> (watch out for dust bytes).
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-8 text-center">
      <img class="mx-auto h-[200px] w-[200px]" src="/assets/construction.gif" alt="Under construction worker" />
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-center font-display text-[1.75rem] tracking-[2px] text-white">NOW UNDER CONSTRUCTION</h2>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
